reviewText: movie came really fast plus i loved the flashbacks it showed of past monster's that lord zedd and rita repulsa created and they had their own halloween bash after being inspired by the people on earth declaring that this was a holiday he could get behind

WHEN LORD ZEDD PEEKSINON THE ANGEL GROVE HIGH SCHOOL HALLAWEEN PARTY, HE DECIDES TO THROW HIS OWN BASH, AFTER ALL. WHOCOULD HOSTA BETTERPARTY THAN THE SUPREME MONSTERMAKER HIMSELF. JOIN LORD ZEDD GOLDAR AND THEIR BUMBLING HENCHMEN AS THEY REMINISCE ABOUT SOME OF THE GREATEST MONSTERS EVER TO BATTLE THE POWER RANGERS. THIS SPECIAL EPISODE FEATURES INCREDIBLE FIGHTING SCENES WITH THE MEANEST AND UGLIEST MONSTERS INCLUDING EYE GUY, SILVER HORNS, THE PUMPKIN RAPPER, SNIZZARD LIPS, THE TERROR TOAD AND MANY MANY MORE.
